Privacy Policy

1. Data Collection

1.1 Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information to improve the app’s performance and provide relevant ads:

* Location: Approximate and precise location
* Device or Other IDs: Device ID, advertising ID
* App Activity: App interactions and usage behavior
* App Info and Performance: Diagnostics and crash reports

1.2 How We Collect Data
Data is collected through standard APIs and third-party services such as Google AdMob.

2. Data Usage
   Collected data is used to:

* Display personalized or contextual ads
* Improve app functionality and user experience
* Analyze performance and fix issues
* Comply with legal and platform requirements

3. Data Sharing and Transfer
   We may share collected data with trusted third parties such as Google AdMob for advertising and analytics. We do not sell user data.

4. Security Measures
   We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect collected data from unauthorized access or misuse.

5. Data Retention
   We retain data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes mentioned above or to comply with legal obligations. Users may request deletion through device settings or by contacting us.

6. Advertising
   This app uses Google AdMob for showing ads. AdMob may collect data such as device ID, advertising ID, and location to serve personalized ads. Users can manage their ad preferences in their Google account settings.

7. Children’s Privacy
   The app is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. Parents are encouraged to supervise their children’s use of mobile apps.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at: sorenavpninfo@gmail.com

Additional Information for Android Users
Sorena VPN complies with Google Play’s Developer Program Policies regarding user data privacy and security.


